# Runtime Schemas Manifest — dist/runtime/schemas/ allowlist
# Only files listed here will be copied into the release package.
# Mirrors the pattern used by runtime/scripts/.dist-include.
# ---
# Format: one filename per line, comments (#) and blank lines ignored.

# ── Phase 1 sub-role envelopes (loaded by validate-phase1-envelope.sh L2 hook) ──
phase1-scan-envelope.schema.json
phase1-research-envelope.schema.json
synthesizer-verdict.schema.json

# ── Legacy alias kept for contract reference ──
# research-envelope.schema.json predates the phase1-* naming convention.
# Retained so external producers/docs that still reference the old path keep working.
research-envelope.schema.json

# ── Cross-phase contract envelopes ──
requirement-packet.schema.json
